Class SampleSizeTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.SampleSizeTree

  • public class SampleSizeTree
extends java.lang.Object

    Class SampleSizeTree

    The SampleSizeTree object contains the whole structure of the sample sizes for both crossed and nested facets, as well management of indices, incrementing indices (stepping), and calculation of of range for each configuration.
    Version:
    %v..%
    Author:
    Ralph Bloch
